nd how to avoid \"invidious\" comparisons which can lead to discouragement or unethical behavior. By the end of this module, you'll be able to attain a better balance between competitive motivation and cooperative satisfaction to make your interactions more productive and successful."]]},"created_time":1645572120000,"last_edited_time":1645602300000,"parent_id":"daf31581-086b-4fb1-9695-5a79117d4300","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","space_id":"bb9288f4-efb5-417f-bf44-1a79fa04feb1"}},"7e5dfcb9-cc30-4ec6-a6e7-d244deb4a546":{"role":"reader","value":{"id":"7e5dfcb9-cc30-4ec6-a6e7-d244deb4a546","version":8,"type":"bookmark","properties":{"link":[["https://d18ky98rnyall9.cloudfront.net/_920fcd4cf1512465c816d08edde8f696_Module-1-Slides.pdf?Expires=1645660800&Signature=U81CZ27R~1Wi~WJKQBHP9-KaOdcXdJSSlxDs7wrPQwMQI8l-ybTSFK2GyWS-yMG~iDL0Jxfd~eWPwF3KI5OwZGNhfZKCT8wCZrzPreCYt0DT0ByDtjjDeuU4yUWtH6HQIRs1L6rDzH~GhdiDUpIXy1n7r6hrdSymENzF-77CvHk_&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJLTNE6QMUY6HBC5A"]]},"created_time":1645601820000,"last_edited_time":1645601820000,"parent_id":"daf31581-086b-4fb1-9695-5a79117d4300","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","space_id":"bb9288f4-efb5-417f-bf44-1a79fa04feb1"}},"0df5a85f-e8d7-4cd9-a85d-e8b024b04a23":{"role":"reader","value":{"id":"0df5a85f-e8d7-4cd9-a85d-e8b024b04a23","version":4,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["In this module, you'll explore how to gain and built trust to develop cooperation, and understand why this critical step can be so challenging. You'll examine the factors that develop a trusting relationship: "],["demonstrating vulnerability, building rapport, and expressing warmth, and learn how to increase trust by uncovering common goals, common enemies, and interdependence. ",[["b"]]],["You'll also learn how to communicate with team members, friends, and opponents in a way that encourages trust. By the end of this module, you’ll understand how to build trusting relationships to achieve cooperation and mutual satisfaction."]]},"created_time":1645572180000,"last_edited_time":1645572180000,"parent_id":"daf31581-086b-4fb1-9695-5a79117d4300","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","space_id":"bb9288f4-efb5-417f-bf44-1a79fa04feb1"}},"ebe104ed-4fc3-4043-bb96-6b0deee9c81b":{"role":"reader","value":{"id":"ebe104ed-4fc3-4043-bb96-6b0deee9c81b","version":8,"type":"bookmark","properties":{"link":[["https://d18ky98rnyall9.cloudfront.net/_97b2c42cff48cb35c2618a116065b29d_Module-2-Slides.pdf?Expires=1645660800&Signature=J5gnPtDQslbPglGntPq26ehDCUgyqq0BMoGCzNHGoVyTZ-QshlFV1qMTFl-OXxtAr9U954IShikUCMfKafCieyyyHGh2BbgbqF6DNCUno5CBeoPYAxUKKDahm5nMUBTrbFNWy47gY1ghy6ee-6xFFthNHQOrHVE-VJum~eUidVQ_&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJLTNE6QMUY6HBC5A"]]},"created_time":1645601820000,"last_edited_time":1645601820000,"parent_id":"daf31581-086b-4fb1-9695-5a79117d4300","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","space_id":"bb9288f4-efb5-417f-bf44-1a79fa04feb1"}},"2b9b5a62-ad26-4894-899a-3c31fe5bf964":{"role":"reader","value":{"id":"2b9b5a62-ad26-4894-899a-3c31fe5bf964","version":4,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["In this module, you’ll learn what deception is, how to detect it, and what to do once you know it's taken place. You'll examine the most common cues that indicate deception and explore practical steps to take when you discover deception. You'll also be able to evaluate deceptions and transgressions to determine whether they are core or non-core violations. Finally, you'll analyze the components of successful apologies, so you can create your own, if necessary. By the conclusion of this module, you'll be able to better detect deception, and devise an appropriate reaction that will help you achieve your objectives."]]},"created_time":1645572180000,"last_edited_time":1645572240000,"parent_id":"daf31581-086b-4fb1-9695-5a79117d4300","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","space_id":"bb9288f4-efb5-417f-bf44-1a79fa04feb1"}},"b950df15-32ff-4127-91b9-a1786ed3c10a":{"role":"reader","value":{"id":"b950df15-32ff-4127-91b9-a1786ed3c10a","version":8,"type":"bookmark","properties":{"link":[["https://d18ky98rnyall9.cloudfront.net/_f16c458af09ad9ce2244bd0e00ffc113_Module-3-Slides.pdf?Expires=1645660800&Signature=Ssaeex8eVPJr~z3hiT4bhZLxsnbMFvPqUf7urwUnzGA7yiftTGxUqsj~Vdnv66L~j-jb5q4rmBxNUZD~KKkuWgqR~WdhC45cm6kI4LYik3YtmwVCJF5xE7h7UWzzyw3mEiw9A8z9SPl7DfdZYAEIcTwB5gXPxHKh~jyiudlo8BQ_&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJLTNE6QMUY6HBC5A"]]},"created_time":1645601820000,"last_edited_time":1645601820000,"parent_id":"daf31581-086b-4fb1-9695-5a79117d4300","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"9e9c4442-4350-473a-b900-c954b0bd7a95","space_id":"bb9288f4-efb5-417f-bf44-1a79fa04feb1"}},"400a6abd-1343-41c8-bd1c-d9ffc2f238cd":{"role":"reader","value":{"id":"400a6abd-1343-41c8-bd1c-d9ffc2f238cd","version":4,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["This module was designed to teach you both the key principles of effective communication, and how to harness the power of setting goals to improve your performance. You’ll lear